02:58.429 --> 02:59.846
- No just stunned.

02:59.847 --> 03:02.349
- Well that worked out nicely.

03:05.853 --> 03:06.979
Are you guys okay?

03:09.189 --> 03:10.690
- I'm fine.

03:10.691 --> 03:12.359
