those stinky old shoes?

03:17.031 --> 03:18.197
- I got my shoes.

03:18.198 --> 03:20.010
- Don't listen to her Samuel.

03:20.034 --> 03:21.076
I'm glad too.

03:22.286 --> 03:24.330
I'm glad you have your shoes.

04:11.251 --> 04:13.313
- Madison what is
wrong with you?

04:13.337 --> 04:14.587
- I'm sorry Roy.

04:14.588 --> 04:15.607
Are you alright?

04:15.631 --> 04:16.524
- Put it in park.

04:16.548 --> 04:18.050
- Oh right, sorry.

04:19.593 --> 04:22.072
- Do you even have a license
to drive this thing?

04:22.096 --> 04:25.116
- Of course I do it's
just that driving

04:25.140 --> 04:28.286
