your picture taken.

04:51.458 --> 04:52.852
- I do not.

04:52.876 --> 04:56.672
And another thing Madison,
is that your doing?

04:59.508 --> 05:02.970
- Have I told you how
nice your mums look?

05:04.388 --> 05:08.994
- Yes, the last time you
tried to change the subject.

05:09.018 --> 05:11.603
- I'll pick up a new trash can.

05:12.479 --> 05:13.479
- Whoa.

05:14.648 --> 05:16.918
