06:01.361 --> 06:02.738
- Loud and clear.

06:05.365 --> 06:06.492
- Morning boss.

06:07.993 --> 06:11.514
Well as your boss and the name
that is on the gallery...

06:11.538 --> 06:15.060
- The Palmer Gallery, the
best in the Midwest.

06:15.084 --> 06:17.710
- It is my job to make
sure our artisans

06:17.711 --> 06:20.379
