06:20.380 --> 06:23.550
- You do a fantastic
job of that Joan.

06:30.224 --> 06:32.893
- Come with me, come on.

06:42.361 --> 06:44.738
Madison do you see this wall?

06:46.115 --> 06:47.406
- Every day.

06:47.407 --> 06:50.576
- Good let that be a
reminder to you that

06:50.577 --> 06:53.831
unless I can fill 16
feet of wall space

06:54.915 --> 06:56.601
with paint and call
it photography

06:56.625 --> 06:59.896
