you my competitors would have.

07:25.112 --> 07:28.174
Madison you're very talented.

07:28.198 --> 07:31.284
One of the best I've seen
in a very long time.

07:31.285 --> 07:32.452
Well since me.

07:35.205 --> 07:36.599
But seriously.

07:36.623 --> 07:39.310
Sometimes you just need
to mat it and frame it.

07:39.334 --> 07:41.460
- I just want it to be perfect.

07:41.461 --> 07:42.462
