09:42.582 --> 09:47.105
- Jesus said I am the
resurrection and I am the life.

09:47.129 --> 09:51.401
Those who believe in me
even though they die

09:51.425 --> 09:53.736
yet they will live.

09:53.760 --> 09:57.931
